metatypes.name: Bearing

metatypes.name: Boots

relationships.name: performedBy
relationships.description: A is performed by B if A is a process (or action) and B is a continuant (non-temporal) entity and B participates in or is involved in A.

relationships.name: performs
relationships.description: A performs B if B is a process and A is a continuant entity and A participates in or is involved in B.

relationships.name: referencedBy
relationships.description: Denotes that the entity (usually an artifact or asset) is referred to by some other entity.

relationships.name: references
relationships.description: Denotes that the entity refers to some other entity, usually an artifact/generically dependent continuant or asset.
